ygData.subject: Twinking
ygData.msgSnippet: I think some twinking is ok. Not huge leaps like the 200 int caster some talk about. I am talking minor twinks...like starting a new character with maybe 10pp.
ygData.messageBody:
I think some twinking is ok. Not huge leaps like
the 200 int caster some talk about. I am talking
minor twinks...like starting a new character with maybe
10pp. You know, enough to buy basic equipment right
from the start. First level spells for instance..maybe
basic armor and weapons.<br><br>I just recently started
playing EQ so no self twinking yet. However, I have been
given items and money from high level characters...is
this considered twinking? Someone doing something nice
just because they could? I am not sure.<br><br>I
really don't know if i would twink myself..the game is
just too darn fun!<br><br>Calidiel Shapeshyfter 20th
season chanter...rodcet nife sever
